Cell[TextData[{"The first argument is the state vector and the second \
argument specifies the dimension of basis (which is computational). The \
default basis is the computational basis, unless specified otherwise. With no \
basis info, the basis is set by default as a ", 
        Cell[BoxData[SuperscriptBox["2", "n"]], "InlineFormula", 
         ExpressionUUID -> "d4b1c5ac-fa2a-4781-a032-a81df4ce722a"], 
        "-dimensional computational basis."}], "ExampleText", 
