Cell["\<\
There are a collection of named quantum state, built-in within Wolfram \
quantum framework. In the following examples, the traditional form is mostly \
shown, rather the corresponding summary box of quantum states. Some times we \
may show the traditional form instead of the summary-box.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912629789644725*^9, 3.912629858363009*^9}, {
  3.987510279028638*^9, 3.987510303655773*^9}},
 CellID->100326036,ExpressionUUID->"ad04566e-81e4-41ed-aa4c-622fd6836d94"],

